# Agent Profiles

Defines AgentProfile, PromptTemplates, and ToolConfig types for configuring agents.

## AgentProfile

Named, reusable agent configuration. Fields: Name, Provider, Command, CLIArgs, Timeout, Retries, RateLimit, PromptTemplates, Tools, Skills, ModelID.

## PromptTemplates

Customizable template strings. Fields: Build, Validate, System.

## ToolConfig

Tool available to agent. Fields: Name, Enabled, Config.
